
Steps Involved In making a machine learning model

1) Problem Definiton               - already defined problem ( already provided )

2) Data Collection                 - Collecting data required to solve the given problem

3) Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA) - Analyse the data neatly 

4) Data Preprocessing / Cleaning   - Cleaning the data to run algorithms for model

5) Feature Selection / Engineering - Extracting required features out of the dataset

6) Split the Dataset 

7) Model Selection

8) Model Training

9) Model Evaluation

10) Hyper Parameter Tuning

11) Model Testing / Validation